Spleep Tracker API - Development
--------------------------------------------


This project is being used for learning Node JS and its Event Loop and non blocking code.
API Endpoints: 

POST:
/sleep-log: 
Create a sleep log

GET: 
/sleep-logs:
List all sleep logs

Goals: 
- Database Integration (Ideally NoSQL)
- User Auth
- Data Validation
- Endpoint for Analytics (Possible Integration with BI)
- Build Front-end
- Deploy Application

NOTE: This is only for learning purpose. Some of these are not really practical production application.

